# arvo-bits-contracts

Bit-level trait contracts for arvo. Declarations of `HasBitWidth`,
`BitAccess`, `BitSequence`, `BitLogic`, `BitPrim`, `UBitContainer`,
`IBitContainer`. All `pub const trait`. Default-method bodies and
blanket-impl targets reference `Bits<N, S>` from `arvo-storage`.
Concrete impls live in `arvo-bits`. `#![no_std]`, no alloc.
